{"tid":256194,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視終於收皮😂😂😂😂😂🤙🏿","createTime":"2017-05-24T10:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T12:30:19.000Z","uid":15236,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5643f034c09d61de2c5d8a44637323580b7a87","tid":256194,"uid":15236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"再次傳出財困的樂視，一直未有影響到香港業務，但樂視體育今日公佈，因節目調整，本週日(5月28日)凌晨在LeSports HK平台直播的英格蘭足總盃(FA Cup)決賽(阿仙奴對車路士)，將無法播出。LeSports HK對本次受影響的用戶鄭重致歉，將提供3個月超級體育組合作為補償。<br />\n<br />\n本報向樂視香港公關查詢無法播放的原因，只獲回覆「因節目調整」，賠償方面亦只得3個月超級體育組合。樂視只表示，如有查詢，可聯繫客戶服務熱線：3956 6666<br />\n<br />\n據了解，與樂視合作播放英超的nowTV並沒有直播的英格蘭足總盃(FA Cup)，如今樂視無法播出，屆時香港可能將沒有合法途徑收看足總盃決賽。<br />\n<br />\n支那野真係信唔撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdccbe2dc419b20cbd1c41380b3ef5227b87f25","tid":256194,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:55:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！！！！！！"},{"pid":"be40ded88cac9013da1a861d42308d04bb417c94","tid":256194,"uid":15236,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母！！！！！！</blockquote><br />\nching吾系有買牙？😅"},{"pid":"ec5925f1b2e2b35ed5bbd4e8364eb278a805215a","tid":256194,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"節目調整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fdc18d51a7f451cdb20c562e792181f54469f5","tid":256194,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"冇波睇送十年又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad412fb6675106b028a8ce2ec304d9d3e2c76fd7","tid":256194,"uid":69528,"like":0,"dislike